    <script type="text/javascript">
        function DoClick(buttonName, e) {

            if ($('#ctl01_UCHeader_txtSearch').val().length > 2) {
                $('#ctl01_UCHeader_txtSearch').autocomplete({
                    source: function (request, response) {
                        $.ajax({
                            url: '/api/search/GetAutoComplete',
                            dataType: "json",
                            data: {
                                text: request.term,
                                IndexName: 'iapps-irem_irem-front-prod'//should probably be dynamic
                            },
                            success: function (data) {
                                if (data != null)
                                    response(data.options);
                                $('.main_nav .search span').hide();
                            },
                            error: function (request, status, error) {
                                console.log(error);
                            }
                        });
                    },
                    minLength: 2
                });
            }

            var key;
            if (window.event)
                key = window.event.keyCode;     //IE
            else
                key = e.which;     //firefox

            if (key == 13) {
                //Get the button the user wants to have clicked
                var btn = document.getElementById(buttonName);
                if (btn != null) { //If we find the button click it
                    btn.click();
                    event.keyCode = 0
                }
            } else {
                return;
            }
        }
    </script>

 <br /><strong>We believe in our people, and we provide the tools they need to succeed.</strong> We open doors, we forge connections, and we help show the way forward. Backed by the power that comes with being an affiliate of the National Association of REALTORS&reg;, we add value to our members, who in turn add value to their teams, their workplaces, and the properties in their commercial and residential portfolios.<br />
 <br />Our memberships empower college students, young professionals, and industry veterans who are committed to career advancement. Earning our credentials, including the CPM, ARM, ACoM, and AMO, demonstrates a commitment to, and passion for, good management. These credentials, along with our courses and array of resources, all exist with one goal in mind – <strong>to make a difference in the careers of those who manage.</strong></p>

	function InitMenu() {



		/*============ Navigation Menu Starts ========================*/
		$('.nav li').hover(function () {
			$('ul.controlMnuNode', $(this, 'ul.nav li')).show();
		}, function () {
			$('ul.controlMnuNode', $(this, 'ul.nav li')).hide()
		})

		$('.controlMnuNode').hover(function () {
			$(this).prev().addClass('active')
		}, function () {
			$(this).prev().removeClass('active')
		})

		// ___________ Updated for Mega Menu [Starts]__________________//

		function equalHeight(group) {
			tallest = 230;
			group.each(function () {
				thisHeight = $(this).height();
				if (thisHeight > tallest) {
					tallest = thisHeight;
				}
			});
			group.height(tallest);
		}


		$('.controlMnuNode').hover(function () {
			equalHeight($(".controlLiCls"));
		})

		// ___________ Updated for Mega Menu [Ends]__________________//


		/*============ Navigation Menu Starts ========================*/

		$(".lftNavLink").hover(function () {
			$('.leftNavSubUl').hide();
			$(this).addClass('active');
			$('.leftNavSubUl li a').removeClass('active');
			$(this).next().show();
		}, function () {
			$(this).next().show();
			$(this).removeClass('active');
		});

		$(".leftNavSubUl").hover(function () {
			$(this).prev().addClass('active');
		}, function () {
			$(this).hide();
			$(this).prev().removeClass('active')
		});

		$("#thumbNail li a").hover(function () {
			$(this).parent().children('.tollTipBox').show();
		}, function () {
			$(this).parent().children('.tollTipBox').hide();
		});

		/*============ Region LeftNav Menu Starts ========================*/

		$(".regionNavLink").hover(function () {
			$('.leftNavSubRegion').hide();
			$(this).addClass('active');
			$('.leftNavSubRegion li a').removeClass('active');
			$(this).next().show();
		}, function () {
			$(this).next().show();
			$(this).removeClass('active');
		});

		$(".leftNavSubRegion").hover(function () {
			$(this).prev().addClass('active');
		}, function () {
			$(this).hide();
			$(this).prev().removeClass('active')
		});

		$("ul.nav li").hover(function () {
			$(this).addClass('navHover');
			$(this).children('a').addClass('navHover');
		}, function () {
			$(this).removeClass('navHover');
			$(this).children('a').removeClass('navHover');
			$('ul.nav li.navActive').addClass('navHover');
			$('ul.nav li.navActive a').addClass('navHover');
		});


		/*============ Tooltip ========================*/

		$(".leftNavSubUl").hover(function () {
			$(this).prev().addClass('active');
		}, function () {
			$(this).hide();
			$(this).prev().removeClass('active')
		});
